@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@apiKey = your-secret-key-here

### Health check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Digest without auth should fail
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/digest

### Digest with auth header
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/digest
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Positive sentiment filter
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/digest?sentiment=positive
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Limit clusters to 3
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/digest?limit=3
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### List all topics
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/topics
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Fetch a topic by name
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/topic/technology
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Missing topic should return 404
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/topic/nonexistent
x-api-key: {{apiKey}}

### Swagger docs
GET {{baseUrl}}/api-docs